      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lvov.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was in the Russia-- us belong with-- for-- to Poland-- you know, Lvov.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they went over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then my brother, my youngest brother, was in--",
